OL,3,C'Much-loved' Welsh politician dies
OL,4,Csuddenly
OL,6,FHefin David, a Welsh Labour politician
OL,7,Fand Member of the Senedd (MS), has
OL,8,Fdied.
OL,10,FThe 47-year-old father of two was
OL,11,Ffirst elected as an MS for Caerphilly
OL,12,Fin 2016 and re-elected in 2021.
OL,14,FHis partner Vikki Howells is the MS
OL,15,Ffor Cynon Valley and minister for
OL,16,Ffurther and higher education in the
OL,17,FWelsh Government.
