OL,3,C'Much-loved' Welsh politician dies
OL,4,Csuddenly
OL,6,FGwent Police said they were called to
OL,7,Fa medical emergency just before 7pm on
OL,8,FTuesday where a 47-year-old man was
OL,9,Ffound unresponsive.
OL,11,FParamedics attended and confirmed the
OL,12,Fman had died. His death is not being
OL,13,Ftreated as suspicious.
OL,15,FIn a statement, Welsh Labour leader
OL,16,Fand First Minister Eluned Morgan paid
OL,17,Ftribute, saying the party is
OL,18,F"extremely saddened by the sudden
OL,19,Fdeath of Hefin."
