OL,6,F"Our thoughts are with his family at
OL,7,Fthis terrible time.
OL,9,F"Hefin was a much-loved member of the
OL,10,FLabour family. He served Caerphilly as
OL,11,Fa councillor and a Member of the
OL,12,FSenedd with pride and passion.
OL,14,F"He was an outstanding politician,
OL,15,Fwarm and enthusiastic and a great
OL,16,Fcommunicator ` especially on behalf of
