OL,6,FThe Llywydd Elin Jones said: "He was a
OL,7,Fpassionate politician, loyal to his
OL,8,Fparty, his country, and constituents.
OL,9,FHe was able to effectively work across
OL,10,Fparties and seek common ground.
OL,12,F"Hefin was particularly well-liked
OL,13,Facross the Senedd. He was our
OL,14,FCommissioner with responsibility for
OL,15,FFinance and undertook that role with
OL,16,Fdiligence and skill.
OL,18,F"The news is devastating and reminds
OL,19,Fus of the fragility of life and the
OL,20,Fneed for us all to support each other."
