OL,6,FIn his role as a MS, he focused on
OL,7,Femployability, access to further and
OL,8,Fhigher education for those with
OL,9,Fadditional needs and the development
OL,10,Fof Valleys communities.
OL,12,FBefore his election to the Senedd, Mr
OL,13,FDavid was a Senior Lecturer at Cardiff
OL,14,FMetropolitan University and served on
OL,15,FCaerphilly Council in 2007 as a
OL,16,Frepresentative for the ward St Cattwg.
OL,18,FHe was also a governor of Heolddu
OL,19,FComprehensive School and Trinity
OL,20,FFields School and a trustee of the
OL,21,FCaerphilly Miners Centre.
