OL,3,C'Much-loved' Welsh politician dies
OL,4,Csuddenly
OL,6,FTributes have been paid to Labour MS
OL,7,FHefin David by politicians from across
OL,8,Fthe Senedd.
OL,10,FAndrew RT Davies, former leader of the
OL,11,FWelsh Conservatives, said:
OL,12,F"Heartbreaking and tragic news that
OL,13,FHefin David, such a young Member of
OL,14,Fthe Senedd with so much to offer and
OL,15,Fgive to Wales and the community he
OL,16,Floved has passed away.
OL,18,FDelyth Jewell, Plaid Cymru MS for the
OL,19,FSouth Wales East region, also wrote of
OL,20,Fher sadness at his death.
