OL,6,FShe said: "The news about Hefin David
OL,7,Fis so desperately tragic. Hefin was
OL,8,Falways steadfast in his views, loyal
OL,9,Fto his roots, and he represented this
OL,10,Farea diligently.
OL,12,F"We were from different parties but
OL,13,Fworked together on many local issues.
OL,14,FI will miss him. What a sad and
OL,15,Fdreadful loss."
